&lt;p&gt;The Majors sales team is responsible for revenue growth in new and existing customers that represent the largest prospective accounts for Samsara by total addressable opportunity. This role can be office-based or fully remote covering a certain geography.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a remote position open to candidates residing in the US.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
